== Fuddareanchem Pustok ==
'''Book of Judges'''

[[File:Maarten van Heemskerck 024.jpg|thumb|"Gideon thanks God for the miracle of the dew", painting by Maarten van Heemskerck (Musée des Beaux-Arts de Strasbourg)]]





'''Fuddareanchem pustok tin barik-mottea vibhagamnim vanttlam :'''

'''I:''' 	Prostavna			Ovesvor 1/1-2/5

'''II:'''	Pustokacho mukhel bhag	Ovesvor 2/6-16/31

'''III :'''	Don purvonnam, poilem mhollear Danitkar dusrea zagear ravunk vetat ani Dev-Sthan bandtat, (polle ovesvor 17-18).  Dusrem mhollear Gibeah-ant zalolea khuna pasot, Benjaminacher zhuz kortat tea vixim .  (polle ovesvor 19-21)

Pustokachea mukhel bhagant Fuddareancho itihas vachunk mellta (2/6-16/31).  Povitr Pustokache
Zannar hea Fuddareank, vhoddle Fuddari  (Major) ani Lhan Fuddari (Minor) – oxem mhonnunontor
kortat.
 
Vhoddle Fuddari (6) he porim : Othniel, ehud, Barak (aniDeborah), Gideon, Jefthan ani Samson.  
Hancheo  soggleancho kornneo bariksannem sangleat.

Lhan Fuddari (6) he porim : Shamgar, (3/31); Tola ani Jari, (10/1-15); Ibzan, Elon ani Abdon, (12/8-15) 
Hanchi choddxi khobor korunk na.

Vhoddle Fuddari porjechi suttka kortat tanche vixim zaiti onto rasa ; tancho oromb, tanchem vhoddponn 
ani kornnio khub toren veglleo asat.  Punn soglleank ek vixeshtai asa ti mhollear : tankam kherit kurpa 
mell’llea, ek vorgunn mell’lla.  Suttka korpachea karia pasot Devanuch tankam venchun kaddleat.

Lhan Fuddari mhollear Tola, Jair, Ibzan, Elon ani Abdon hanche vixim chodd mahiti na.  tannim konnachi 
tori suttka kelea mhonn mellona.  Tancho oromb,  tanchea kuttumbachi khobor ani tankam khoinchea 
zagear purleat, itlem mat boroilolem mellta.



