'''Israelitank, hea pustokacho mukhel sondex ho :''' 

Lok odhormi zalolean Devan piddapidd dhaddun tankam 
Xikxa dili ani jedna tim Deva sorxim portolim tedna tankam zoit favo zalem. Sirakachea Pustokacho 
borovpi Fuddareanche thiraie pasot tankam vakhannta (polle Sir. 46/11-12).  Toxench Hebrevank 
boroilole chittint, tanchea bhavarthak lagun ies mell’lla mhonn dakhoita (polle Heb. 11/32-34; 12/1).

